Brengsek.

165
00:10:52,382 --> 00:10:54,926
Jantungku rasanya mau
copot dari dada.

166
00:10:55,009 --> 00:10:57,428
Kenapa sih
dia memelukku seperti itu?

167
00:10:59,597 --> 00:11:00,848
Apakah kamu tidak membawa payung?

168
00:11:00,932 --> 00:11:01,891
